{"tid":2122452,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來雞姦同大巴今季互含左51次","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:59:51.000Z","uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c566b75bab5939cfdb535dca91c1d6db9dfd8d","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:09:13.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯教練沙利認為，基斯坦奴朗拿度與迪巴拿這對拍檔可以更上一層樓。<br />\n<br />\n基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）在上季加盟祖雲達斯後，跟迪巴拿（Paulo Dybala）未能好好合作，後者更幾近於去年夏天離隊。不過，兩人最近終於擦出火花，意甲重啟後直接及間接合力貢獻了17球。<br />\n<br />\n「這證明了我們可以有進步空間。我看不到C朗及迪巴拿這樣的世界級球員同時在場會有甚麼難處，他們在今季已經轟入51球！」沙利（Maurizio Sarri）表示。<br />\n<br />\n祖記很大機會完成意甲9連霸，但沙利坦言C朗毋須休息：「我10分鐘前跟他傾談過，他說自己很fit。這正是他犀利的地方，在體能及心理回復得非常快，很快就可以重新訂立下個目標。」"},{"pid":"eaa842dade284a69b119b60f5b91be4cae41d423","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YnmcxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YnmcxB.png&h=2817102c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到都覺得屎忽痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965c7bc99e53c38df9e126b73931a4780241a738","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"C朗毋須休息，我10分鐘前跟他傾談過，他說自己很fit。這正是他犀利的地方，在體能及心理回復得非常快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750e7783c17357d74214e4403091623f06502d7c","tid":2122452,"uid":74164,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"有帶BRA拿呢D做隊長 我呀婆都唔止拎意甲 拎埋世界杯添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeef417357fc6b5d207ad4b97b0bb3b3aede935","tid":2122452,"uid":268486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"中左武肺仲勁左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c