須從中學到教訓，並努力保持自己的風格。」"},{"pid":"b2c71e961898f4ab845e76dafb59f480e4ebae39","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c95edb2e4e54df8ac29c785f161718d7183de02","tid":2122452,"uid":261172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"11fd566fb65fcae1f2eecb8fe8b3e82fa2cee7f1","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed10ef3f1f9439e2f47e9a34880dd9ecdd323c3b","tid":2122452,"uid":261172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我看不到C朗及迪巴拿這樣的世界級球員同時在場會有甚麼難處</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚搶口呀沙爹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"好撚勁喎沙蛇<br />\n輸烏甸1:2<br />\n歐聯落後法甲中游里昂2:0<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"車路士在禁錮舒服佐<br />\n<br />\n有佐仔的話沙爹使驚你?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"佐仔不孝兒，唔去垃圾蛆跟爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9da58c3d26ebafa1f1d0dacdb83078442b50c4e","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf07a76767a501668df17af888ff7203dec0d7ac","tid":2122452,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"阿特蘭大 一百球都黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"呢個就真係勁喇，成套進攻模式幾有前瞻性"},{"pid":"7d946c895ac9629d9c5fddf56786f143c0ba7677","tid":2122452,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448e5d